  <brief_title>Clinical, Molecular and Metabolic Characteristics of Parkinson's Disease (PD) Patients With Parkin Mutation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Clinical, Molecular and Metabolic Characteristics of PD Patients With and Without Parkin Mutation</official_title>
